CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1946 reads: "Bridge Experts Meet In Pittsburgh - During the national tournament at the American Bridge Association now meeting in Pittsburgh, national officials posed for The Courier cameraman at Kay Boys' Club where the tournament is being held. Top picture is of the four lieutenants from Lockbourne Army Air Base, Columbus, Ohio, who played as a team; left to right, Lieuts. Samuel Lynn, Francis Collier, Marion Mann, and Heber Houston....Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Full length group portrait of four lieutenants, left to right, Samuel Lynn, Francis Collier, Marion Mann, and Heber Houston, from Lockbourne Army Air Base, Columbus, Ohio
